
makes app folder for django, main dir
django-admin startproject music_controller

inside music_controller
django-admin startapp api

init django database( less boiler plate code more fun code), you will see dn.sqlite3
py .\manage.py makemigrations
py .\manage.py migrate

backend server running
py .\manage.py runserver

py -m venv nameOfEnv
.\env\Scripts\activate


WHY serlizers matter in API
converts complex data types ( querysets  model instances) into Python data types ( dictionaries) that can be rendered into JSON or XML, and vice versa


install everything you need all at once
pip install -r .\requirments.txt


django use obj relational mapper which adds a layer of obtraction to datanases
so we write py code and it interacts with the database makes life better
